kpi_info.title: period_duration (period_duration)
kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: CCH_DATA_CELL_UL (M5002C0)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transferred in RACH in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. UPDATED:The counter is updated when the connection is released or the measurement interval ends. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: EDCH_DATA_SCELL_UL (M5002C2)
kpi_info.use: Amount of MAC-e PDU data transferred in the E-DCH serving cell in the uplink direction during the measurement interval. The MAC-e header includes to the MAC-e PDU data calculation. This counter is also used for MAC-i PDU data amount calculation.The MAC-i header includes to the MAC-i PDU data calculation. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the connection is released or the measurement interval ends. Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: EDCH_DATA_NSC_S_EDCH_UL (M5002C3)

Note: This counter doesn't have a formula and the default (SUM) was used.

kpi_info.title: MC_HSDPA_DATA_ACK_PRI (M5002C126)
kpi_info.use: Total amount of positively acknowledged MC HSDPA data sent on MAC-ehs PDUs in the primary cell. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the MAC-ehs PDU is positively acknowledged in the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: MC_HSDPA_DATA_ACK_SEC (M5002C127)
kpi_info.use: Total amount of positively acknowledged MC HSDPA data sent on MAC-ehs PDUs in all secondary cells. UPDATED:The counter is updated when the MAC-ehs PDU is positively acknowledged in all secondary cells. The counter is updated only in the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: MC_HSDPA_ORIG_DATA_PRI (M5002C128)
kpi_info.use: Total amount of MC HSDPA original data (first transmissions) sent on MAC-ehs PDUs in the primary cell. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the MAC-ehs PDU is sent to the air in the primary cell (first transmission of the PDU only).

kpi_info.title: MC_HSDPA_ORIG_DATA_SEC (M5002C129)
kpi_info.use: Total amount of MC HSDPA original data (first transmissions) sent on MAC-ehs PDUs in all secondary cells. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the MAC-ehs PDU is sent to the air in all secondary cells (first transmission of the PDU only). The counter is updated only in the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: HSDPA_ORIG_DATA (M5002C130)
kpi_info.use: Total amount of HSDPA original data (first transmissions) sent on MAC-hs/ehs PDUs. This counter includes legacy single carrier, MC and MIMO HSDPA data. UPDATED:The counter is updated when the MAC-hs/ehs PDU is sent to the air (first transmission of the PDU only). In case of MC, the counter is updated only in the primary cell.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_DL_EFACH (M5002C50)
kpi_info.use: DL User Data volume in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the DL User Plane data is sent by the MAC-ehs scheduler to the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: C_DATA_VOL_DL_EFACH (M5002C51)
kpi_info.use: DL Control Data volume in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the DL Control Plane data is sent by the MAC-ehs scheduler to the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_TR_TIME_DL_EFACH (M5002C52)
kpi_info.use: Time need to transmit DL User Data in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated by the value of transmission time when the DL User Plane data is sent by the MAC-ehs scheduler to the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: C_DATA_TR_TIME_DL_EFACH (M5002C53)
kpi_info.use: Time need to transmit DL Control Data in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated by the value of transmission time when the DL Control Plane data is sent by the MAC-ehs scheduler to the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_UL_EFACH (M5002C54)
kpi_info.use: UL User Data volume in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the UL User Plane data is received to the MAC-i scheduler from the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: C_DATA_VOL_UL_EFACH (M5002C55)
kpi_info.use: UL Control Data volume in Enhanced Cell FACH state. UPDATED: The counter is updated when the UL Control Plane data is received to the MAC-i scheduler from the UE which is in Enhanced CELL_FACH state.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_TR_TIME_UL_EFACH (M5002C56)

kpi_info.title: C_DATA_TR_TIME_UL_EFACH (M5002C57)

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_DL_DEF_PRIO_AAR (M5002C131)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the downlink direction with default SPI. Default SPI is the one that is received from the RNC in NBAP RL Setup/Reconfiguration message. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE and multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell. UPDATED: The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with default SPI. The counter is pegged even if the feature "Application aware RAN" is disabled for the cell.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_DL_INC_PRIO_AAR (M5002C132)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the downlink direction with promoted SPI, that is, any SPI value that is higher than the default SPI. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE and multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell. UPDATED:The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with higher SPI than default.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_DL_DEC_PRIO_AAR (M5002C133)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the downlink direction with demoted SPI, that is, any SPI value that is lower than the default SPI. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE and multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell. UPDATED:The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with lower SPI than default.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_UL_DEF_PRIO_AAR (M5002C134)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the uplink direction with default SPI. Default SPI is the one that is received from RNC in NBAP RL Setup/Reconfiguration message. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell and not the cases of multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE. UPDATED:The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with default SPI. The counter is pegged even if the feature "Application aware RAN" is disabled for the cell.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_UL_INC_PRIO_AAR (M5002C135)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the uplink direction with promoted SPI, that is, any SPI value that is higher than the default SPI. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell and not the cases of multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE. UPDATED: The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with higher SPI than default.

kpi_info.title: U_DATA_VOL_UL_DEC_PRIO_AAR (M5002C136)
kpi_info.use: Amount of data transmitted in the uplink direction with demoted SPI, that is, any SPI value that is lower than the default SPI. The counter considers all cases of single PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE in the cell and not the cases of multiple PS NRT MAC-d queues per UE. UPDATED: The counter is incremented when data is transmitted with lower SPI than default.
